00:00:02.168 --> 00:00:05.005
3SL油管接頭卡鉗總泵灌油安裝教學
Helix 3/3.1/3SL/3CARBON Hydraulic Disc Brake Installation Instruction

00:00:05.505 --> 00:00:08.008
所需工具
tools

00:00:09.743 --> 00:00:22.022
用手把油管螺絲輕輕鎖住
braking oil onto the oil bleeder hole at a torque of 2~3Nm

00:00:24.491 --> 00:00:28.028
再使用8mm開口板手將油管鎖付於總泵
Use 8mm adjustable wrench to fasten the connecting bolt on the master cylinder 

00:00:28.661 --> 00:00:33.066
油管螺絲鎖緊扭力6-8Nm
tighten the hose on to the master cylinder with an 8mm wrench at a torque of 6-8Nm

00:00:36.603 --> 00:00:46.613
將注油螺絲於胡琴接頭兩側分別放置O環
Penetrate the Banjo bolt through the Banjo insert with O-ring on each side

00:00:50.917 --> 00:01:00.927
將胡琴接頭鎖設於卡鉗
and fasten on the caliper

00:01:03.329 --> 00:01:12.005
使用鈕力板手鎖緊鈕力6-8Nm
at a torque of 6-8Nm

00:01:15.241 --> 00:01:21.014
M6xP1x18前叉螺絲+華司將符合規格
tighten the qualified adaptor on the front fork or frame by M6XP1X18 adaptor fixing bolt

00:01:23.717 --> 00:01:29.022
之轉接座鎖接在前叉或車架上

00:01:31.658 --> 00:01:36.996
將轉接座安裝於前叉與車架上即可

00:01:56.850 --> 00:02:02.022
將卡鉗安裝於轉接座上,但不要鎖緊
Install the calipers on the adaptor by M6 calipers fixing bolt (2pcs) loosely

00:02:03.523 --> 00:02:07.027
但不要鎖緊
and let calipers be able to swivel left and right for adjusting its position.

00:02:08.762 --> 00:02:18.738
使卡鉗能夠自由左右調整其位置即完成
END

